        {
            "title": "全日收市｜港股突破上午高位  收復10天線  藥明系午後揚",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股午後向好，升破上午高位，全日升175點，收復10天線(現處25838)及100天線(現處25806)，藥明系午後揚升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"藥明官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1140x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230823_FI_source-web_藥明生物.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"藥明官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1140x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230823_FI_source-web_藥明生物.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">藥明官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數全日報25935，升175點或0.68%，今早開市報25804點，升43點或0.17%，中段見25649，跌111點或0.43%，為半日低位，午後升破上午高位，最高見25990，升230點或0.89%，為全日高位。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數全日報5615，升80點或1.45%，今早開報5546點，升11點或0.21%；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數全日報9106點，升77點或0.86 %，今早以9051點開市，升23點或0.26%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指全日報25951，升210點或0.82%，高水15點 ; 科指期貨報5625，升95點或1.72%，高水10 點 ; 國指期貨報9105，升85點或0.94%，低水1點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市全日成交1793.06億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生生科指數收報15555，升377點或2.49%，藥明系造好，藥明生物(02269)升7.09%，報32.94元，為表現最佳藍籌股 ; 藥明康德(02359)升5.44%，報102.7元 ; 藥明合聯(02268)升7.51%，報68元，為表現最佳生科指數成份股 ; 微創機器人(02252)升5.48%，報23.88元 ; 映恩生物(09606)揚升5.28%，報342.8元 ; 康方生物(09926)升4.4%，報123.4元 ; 金斯瑞生物(01548)升5.12%，報15.2元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">機械人概念股炒上，三花智控(02050)收升7.7%，報34.96元 ; 地平線機器人(09660)升6.97%，報8.29元；越疆(02432)升幅收窄至0.87%，報39.26元；優必選(09880)升3.66%，報113.3元；首程控股(00697)升2.5%，報2.06元；特朗普政府考慮在明年發布扶持AI機械人行業的行政指令，美股機械人概念股爆升。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">科技股個別發展，攜程(09961)升3.93%，報556元，為最強勢藍籌股；小米(01810)升4.38%，報41.98元 ; 美團(03690)彈2.29%，報98.1元 ; 龍頭股阿里巴巴(09988)升0.52%，報154.4元 ; 騰訊(00700)升0.16%，報612元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">申洲國際(02313)跌4.71%，報66.75元，為最弱藍籌股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金沙中國(01928)跌1.56%，報21.46元，跌幅藍籌中居第二位 ; 銀河娛樂(00027)跌0.93%，報40.32元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港鐵(00066)跌1.26%，報31.32元，跌幅藍籌股中居第三位。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15480252-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%bd%9c%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e7%aa%81%e7%a0%b4%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%88%e9%ab%98%e4%bd%8d-%e6%94%b6%e5%be%a910%e5%a4%a9%e7%b7%9a-%e8%97%a5%e6%98%8e%e7%b3%bb%e5%8d%88",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-5.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-04 16:35:35",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "遇見小麵、天域半導體明首掛  暗盤初段齊失守配股價",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">遇見小麵(02408)與天域半導體(02658)明天將首日掛牌，兩新股暗盤初段雙雙失守招股價。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：天域半導體初步招股書\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241224_FI_source-web_TYSiC.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：天域半導體初步招股書\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241224_FI_source-web_TYSiC.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：天域半導體初步招股書</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至下午約4時25分，遇見小麵在輝立交易平台暗盤作價約5.93元，較招股價上限7.04元低 逾15；富途交易平台顯示暗盤價則為6元，亦較招股價低逾14%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">天域半導體在輝立交易平台暗盤約49.5元，較招股價58元低逾15%；富途交易平台顯示的暗盤價為19.7元，低於招股價低逾14%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15480331-%e9%81%87%e8%a6%8b%e5%b0%8f%e9%ba%b5%e3%80%81%e5%a4%a9%e5%9f%9f%e5%8d%8a%e5%b0%8e%e9%ab%94%e6%98%8e%e9%a6%96%e6%8e%9b-%e6%9a%97%e7%9b%a4%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e9%bd%8a%e5%a4%b1%e5%ae%88%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251117_FI_source-web_XN-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-04 16:30:27",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "交投縮減 滬指轉跌2點 深指收復萬三關收升0.4% 芯片股穩步揚",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市午後持續橫行，滬深兩市交投縮減至不足1.55萬億元(人民幣‧下同)。機器人概念固然持續強勢，芯片股亦穩步向上。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"華虹半導體官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01347-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"華虹半導體官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01347-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">華虹半導體官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早表現反覆，由低位3859點時跌18點，到最高3888點時升10點，中午以接近原地踏步收場，午後進入窄幅橫行局面，一直在3869點之上不足10點徘徊；滬指最後收報3875點，跌2點或0.06%，成交降至6237.13億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指形勢相若，同樣是在早市略為波動，但從低位12881點、跌73點，到高位13042點、升87點，波幅亦僅161點，午市全程報升，卻只在萬三點上下整固，早市波幅進一步收窄至僅約50點；深指最後企穩在萬三點之上收市，報13006點，升51點或0.4%，成交不足萬億，只得9252.47億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數升15點或0.34%，以4546點收市；創業板指數升30點或1.01%，報3067點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-8.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-8.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">芯片股全日穩步向上，華虹(01347)A股(688347.SH)收升6.07%，報111.84元；中芯國際(00981)A股(688981.SH)則升2.79%，報114.73元。AP芯片概念股寒武紀(688256.SH)也升2.76%，報1369元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國政府據報會全力支持機器人行業加快發展，令人憧憬繼AI之後，機器人產業將成為下一個快速發展的板塊。機器人概念今早乘機炒上，三花智控(02050)A股(002050)收升7.51%，報44.79元，成交144.82億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">其他機器人概念股亦普遍揚升，巨輪智能(002031.SZ)升約10%後封板，恒而達(300946.SZ)午後升幅擴大至20%後亦漲停板；江蘇雷利(300660.SZ)升幅收窄至8.82%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15480047-%e4%ba%a4%e6%8a%95%e7%b8%ae%e6%b8%9b-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e8%bd%89%e8%b7%8c2%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e5%be%a9%e8%90%ac%e4%b8%89%e9%97%9c%e6%94%b6%e5%8d%870-4-%e8%8a%af%e7%89%87%e8%82%a1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-ap_China-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-04 15:15:28",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股升破上午高位   晶片股升幅擴大  機器人股續炒",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股升破上午高位，現升25876，升115點或0.45%，為暫時高位   ; 恒生科技指數升62點或1.12%，報5596   ; 恒生國企指數升57點或0.63%，報 9085。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交1323.48億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)跌0.16%，報610元; 阿里巴巴(09988)轉升，現升0.07%，報153.7元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">小米(01810)升3.78%，報41.74元，總裁盧偉冰指幾個季度前已開始AI新戰略。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">地平線機器人(09660)升6.58%，報8.26元 ; 三花智控(02050)升7.82%，報35元，優必選(09880)升3.48%，報113.1元，俱入20大成交。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">晶片股升，中芯(00981)升2.9%，報69.15元 ; 華虹(01347)升3.52%，報76.55元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15479957-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%87%e7%a0%b4%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%88%e9%ab%98%e4%bd%8d-%e6%99%b6%e7%89%87%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%87%e5%b9%85%e6%93%b4%e5%a4%a7-%e6%a9%9f%e5%99%a8%e4%ba%ba%e8%82%a1%e7%ba%8c%e7%82%92",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-6.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-04 14:55:29",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
